"use client"

import { useEffect, useState } from "react"
import {
  Loader2,
  CheckCircle,
  PlusCircle,
  AlertCircle,
  ShoppingBag,
  DollarSign,
  Coffee,
  Clock,
  TrendingUp,
  Users,
  ArrowUpRight,
  BookOpen,
  CreditCard,
  Settings,
  Search,
} from "lucide-react"
import "./Content.css"
import { Dashboard, DashboardSection } from "./Dashboard/Dashboard"
import UserManagement from "./UserSection"
import OrdersManagement from "./OrderSection"

const Content = ({ selectedPage }) => {

    switch (selectedPage) {
        case "dashboard":
        return <Dashboard />
        case "user":
        return <UserManagement />
        case "menu":
        return <DashboardSection title="Menu Management" icon={<BookOpen className="h-5 w-5" />} />
        case "order":
        return <OrdersManagement />
        case "payment":
        return <DashboardSection title="Payment Management" icon={<CreditCard className="h-5 w-5" />} />
        case "settings":
        return <DashboardSection title="Settings" icon={<Settings className="h-5 w-5" />} />
        default:
        return <Dashboard />
    }
}

export default Content
